com.microsoft.azure.storage.blob

Class SASQueryParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.storage.blob.SASQueryParameters

  • public final class SASQueryParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the components that make up an Azure Storage SAS' query parameters. NOTE: Instances of this class are immutable.
